text: Teamo Supremo in Maximumpopovision, otherwise known as simply Teamo Supremo, is an American animated television series. It was created by Phil Walsh. It was animated in the limited animation style pioneered by Jay Ward, predecessors which inspired its style. It tells of four superhero children in the near future, who are Captain Llandnarc-Crandall, Skate Lad Hector Felip√© Corrio, Rope Girl Brenda and Diaper Dude Barclae. The series ran from January 19, 2002 to August 17, 2004.
